    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts RHI within 12% of experimental measurements across all operating points, with RH < 1 satisfied at worst-case condition. Pressure-head predictions within 4.3% mean error. The credibility body of evidence supports use of the CFD model to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
